description:
An add-on for ACE COMBAT™ 7: SKIES UNKNOWN.
This set contains the following:

Playable Aircraft: FB-22 Strike Raptor
A stealth fighter based on the F-22 with improved explosive firepower.
Its main delta wings allow it to take on a greater weaponry load, improving its anti-ground offensive capabilities over the original model without losing any of its anti-air capabilities.
With an expanded weapon bay, this improved fighter now boasts greater heavy bomber capabilities and can endure protracted battles.
This set also includes 7 skins, including the special Flash Skin.

This aircraft can equip the XSDB, LAAM, or SFFS as its special weapon.
name: ACE COMBAT™ 7: SKIES UNKNOWN - FB-22 Strike Raptor Set
